message: Chihiro: "You don't have to hold back, Shota-chan."
Shota: "But, but, Chihiro, you still haven't..."
I've hardly been able to reach climax lately.
Just having him inside me makes me happy.
Because I love Shota-chan so much.
Even when he's tired, he loves me with all his might.
He's a little timid, but he's a very kind person.
I'm genuinely glad that I married him.
Chihiro: "I... feel good... I'm feeling it... ahn... ah... ah..."
The words came up to my throat.
Shota-chan doesn't want a child yet.
And I don't want to bother him even if there's a slight chance.
